Class DistanceWeightedKPE

java.lang.Object
  xxl.core.relational.tuples.AbstractTuple

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<DistanceWeightedKPE>, Convertable, Tuple
public class DistanceWeightedKPE
extends KPE
implements java.lang.Comparable<DistanceWeightedKPE>

A DistanceWeightedKPE wraps KPE-objects and additionally contains information on the distance of the KPE-descriptor from some query-object. Objects of this class are used in NearestNeighborQuery to reduce the computational amount of repeatedly determining the distance of KPEs to some query-object.

DistanceWeightedKPE-objects can be compared according to their distance.
